videos.description: Fred VanVleet cruises straight to the basket for a bucket and a foul.

videos.headline: VanVleet flies in for and-1

videos.description: Kevin Durant bounces a pass to Kyrie Irving under the basket for a layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Durant feeds Kyrie for layup) 2021/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Durant feeds Kyrie for layup

videos.description: Bruce Brown inbounds the ball to Kevin Durant, who gets to the rim for the jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Durant gets the dunk off inbounds pass) 2021/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Durant gets the dunk off inbounds pass

videos.description: Kyle Lowry pulls up from long range and sinks the 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lowry drops in 3-pointer from the wing) 2021/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lowry drops in 3-pointer from the wing

videos.description: Kyrie Irving lobs it up to DeAndre Jordan, who gets up to finish the alley-oop.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyrie feeds Jordan for the alley-oop) 2021/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyrie feeds Jordan for the alley-oop

videos.description: Kevin Durant heads back to the locker room as the NBA has deemed he cannot finish the game due to health and safety protocols.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Durant forced to leave due to health and safety protocols) 2021/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Durant forced to leave due to health and safety protocols

videos.description: Kevin Durant receives the news that he has to leave the game due to health and safety protocols and is visibly upset as he walks to the locker room.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Durant upset after being forced to leave game) 2021/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Durant upset after being forced to leave game

videos.description: Kyle Lowry hits a step-back 3-pointer, then follows it up with another long-range triple on the next possession.
videos.headline: Lowry drains back-to-back 3-pointers

videos.description: Kevin Durant is pulled in the third quarter of the Nets' loss to the Raptors, and Adrian Wojnarowski details the reasons why that decision was made.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (The full story behind KD being pulled because of health and safety protocols) 2021/02/05 ESHEET
